Whaddupppp! Soo here’s part two of the series with relationship and sex therapist dr Kate.

For the people who missed this the first time, I’ll give u a brief rundown. I get a shit ton of messages about relationships and sex. I know i don’t know shit about that. I decided to get a sex and relationship therapist to answer ur questions. It’s better than me starting a podcast. Trust me lol. This is supposed to be value add content for you guys. Plus I’m the only one doing thissss hollaaaaaaa 😂 
I named it the no name show (we’ll fix the graphic lol) because i want the sole focus to be on the substance and not for pure entertainment...i also plan on expanding this portfolio 🙌🙏🙌🙏 Again, appreciate those that DM’d me questions, including those whose questions we couldn’t fit into the program (it’s only 10 min).... Feel free to dm us more questions. It’s going to be anonymous—the therapist won’t see your same (i’ll see it but I’ll Block it out before i send it to her for you guys).
